800000275:
参赛规则：
1.创建房间：当前房间上一场已经结算完毕就可创建房间；
2.参加人数：2-4；
3.进入条件：输入正确的房间号，上一场未开始或已结算；
4.开始条件：房间内所有人全部点选准备自动开始；
Rules: 
1. Room creation: room can be created if the previous room has been settled. 
umber of participants: 2-4; 
3. Entry conditions: enter the correct room number; not started or settled in the previous session; 
4. Start condition: all people in the room will start automatically when they click the button.
800000276:
游戏规则：
1.游戏开始后，每个玩家免费获得2000发子弹或4000发子弹，发炮过程中不会消耗金币；
2.在开炮时间内击杀鱼可获得“炮台倍数 X 鱼的倍率”的积分，所有玩家子弹≤0或发炮倒数（8分钟或16分钟）结束时，则结算本次游戏；
3.积分相同的玩家，先达到的排名在前；
4.炮台的倍数会随着玩家剩余子弹数的减少而逐渐提升，炮台倍数跟玩家是否解锁该炮倍无关；
5.房间开启后，在12小时内不开始游戏，房间会自动关闭，房卡通过邮件退还；
Game rules: 
1. After the game starts; each player will get 2000 rounds or 4000 rounds for free; and no fish COINS will be consumed during the shooting process; 
2. Kill the fish in the opening time can obtain the score of (the multiple of X fish in battery). When all players finish the game; the bullet is no more than 0 or the countdown (8 minutes or 16 minutes). 
3. The player with the same score is ranked first; 
4. The multiple of the battery will increase gradually with the reduction of the player's remaining number of bullets. 
5. After the room is opened; the game will not start within 12 hours. The room will be automatically closed and the room card will be returned by mail.
